# Typescript and React

Helpful website
- https://fettblog.eu/typescript-react/getting-started/ 

- npm install -D typescript
- npx tsc -- init
- change the tsconfig file (see file in the same folder)
- npm install -D @types/react @types/react-dom @types/reach__router
- .tsx is required for typescript
- npm install -D tslint tslint-react tslint-config-prettier